name: Trichem Laboratories
overview: Trichem Laboratories was established in the year 1998 at Bengaluru in Karnataka, India. We are engaged in manufacturing and supplying a wide range of poultry feed, antibiotic and veterinary supplement. These products are offered in various specifications and compositions as per the needs of the clients. Our products are antibacterial and anti fungal thus, protects animals from different ailments and are praised for their purity, proven results and unhampered packaging. The main criterion that determines success is the effectiveness of our products. We take the valuable opinion of veterinary and pharmaceutical experts before deciding the formulations of our products. We primarily aim to achieve highest quality standards and supply finest products in the market.
